                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "tfGBe",
                      "name": "dd2",
                      "fill": "#334155",
                      "content": "Ja",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "dnqnc",
                      "name": "dt3",
                      "fill": "#1e293b",
                      "content": "Auswahlverfahren",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "pogFo",
                      "name": "dd3",
                      "fill": "#334155",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "For grade 5 (grundständig): Grundschule prognosis of at least 2.2, a motivational letter from the student, and an admission interview with the principal. For grade 7: sum of grades in Deutsch, Mathematik and Englisch across the year-5 report and mid-year grade-6 report must not exceed 14. A lateral entry (Quereinstieg) is possible in principle if a place is available, primarily in grades 7–8 with French or Russian as the second foreign language. Entry to the Oberstufe requires MSA plus grade-10 promotion certificate; newcomers must additionally demonstrate basic knowledge of Judaism.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "vzCgq",
                      "name": "dt4",
                      "fill": "#1e293b",
                      "content": "Probeunterricht",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "08f6c",
                      "name": "dd4",
                      "fill": "#334155",
                      "content": "Ja",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "S2D5A",
                      "name": "dt5",
                      "fill": "#1e293b",
                      "content": "Aufnahmetest",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "64Rnp",
                      "name": "dd5",
                      "fill": "#334155",
                      "content": "Ja",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "EHdFB",
                      "name": "dtHinweise",
                      "fill": "#1e293b",
                      "content": "Hinweise",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "3mEA3",
                      "name": "ddHinweise",
                      "fill": "#334155",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Probeunterricht is available in cases where the required Förderprognose is missing (grade 7 entry). Admission interview (Aufnahmegespräch) is required for the grundständig grade-5 track. Hebrew is mandatory for all students in grades 5–10 regardless of religious background; lateral entrants without Hebrew must take a remedial course. The school is a state-recognised private Jewish school; all students (Jewish and non-Jewish) participate in Hebrew and Jewish religious education and kosher lunch. Approximately 70% of students are Jewish.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
